@node Main "Permu - Documentation"

                               'Permu' 1.04

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Permu' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you try to match a pattern
of tiles shown at the upper right in the game window in the least
amount of moves possible.

  You can choose any game board size you like, from a 4 by 4 tiles
board, up to a 9 by 9 tiles board size.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
               @{"          History          " link histo}
               @{"        Legal stuff        " link legal}
               @{"          Credits          " link credits}


@{b}NOTE@{ub}: 'Permu' is @{"SHAREWARE" link mrware} so if you like and use it, please
